To load a sample in [[Ultrabeat]] follow these steps.

'''1.''' First choose the key you want the sample to be placed on.The keys are to the left of the module.Click on one.

'''2.''' Select Sample from the menu in the lower left-center of the module.

'''3.''' Click the tiny arrow in the upper left of the sample display that appears.

'''4.''' Select the sample you want to load from the menu that appears.


[[File:Logic ultrabeat sample load.png]]



==Note==

If you can't hear the sample when you play it try turning off (or changing the settings of) the filter. You can do this by clicking the word ''filter'' in the center of the module.

